  <div class="column_holder">
    <h1>
      <img alt="JOBS" src="/images/headers/pf_heading/dynamicimage.aspx?text=JOBS" />
    </h1>
    <div class="column_heading">
      <span id="ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_lblTop"><p>GRIN is constantly looking for talented people. All available positions are listed below. Apply via the form or by e-mail.  If you are interested in a position that isn&rsquo;t listed, please send your CV via e-mail to jobs@grin.se.</p></span></div>
    <div class="column_sep">
      <img src="img/jobs/jobs_open_sep.png" alt="Open positions" /></div>
    
    
      <div class="column_content">
        <h1>
          <img alt="Thursday 06 March 2008" src="/images/headers/pf_small/dynamicimage.aspx?text=Thursday 06 March 2008" />
        </h1>
        <h2>
          <img alt="IT-technician/QA, Gothenburg" src="/images/headers/pf_heading/dynamicimage.aspx?text=IT-technician/QA, Gothenburg" />
        </h2>
        <p>
          <span id="ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_lblJobText"><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">We are looking for a combined IT-technician/Quality Assurance tester for the Gothenburg Studio to work on a major title on the next Gen Platforms and PC.&nbsp;<br />
</span><span lang="EN-US"><br />
Work as part time IT-support , and part time as part of the internal QA team, testing products on all home console platforms. </span><span lang="EN-US">Maintain and update the bug database. </span><span lang="EN-US">Work closely with the development team in identifying, resolving and verifying issues. </span><span lang="EN-US">Keep up to date with the latest standards of console manufacturers. </span><span lang="EN-US">Be involved with projects from concept through completion.<br />
</span><span><strong><br />
Requirements<br />
</strong>&bull; Up to date knowledge of and experience with bug database software&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />
</span><span lang="EN-US">&bull; Working knowledge of testing processes &amp; documentation<br />
</span><span lang="EN-US">&bull; Education within the area or have a shipped title.&nbsp;<br />
</span><span lang="EN-US">&bull; Basic understanding of Maya, Max &amp; Photoshop<br />
</span><span lang="EN-US">&bull; Basic understanding of programming<br />
</span><span lang="EN-US">&bull; Able to help out with various IT tasks, both hardware and software<br />
</span><span lang="EN-US">&bull; Have experience of the 360 and PS3 platforms<br />
</span><span lang="EN-US">&bull; Highly motivated and be a true team player<br />
</span><span lang="EN-US">&bull; Have strong written and verbal communication skills<br />
</span><span lang="EN-US">&bull; Have good analytical skills and an eye for detail<br />
</span><span lang="EN-US">&bull; Be methodical, thorough and organized<br />
</span><span lang="EN-US">&bull; Understand the technical restrictions of games development&nbsp;<br />
</span><span lang="EN-US">&bull; Excellent English skills. Both written and verbal<br />
</span><span lang="EN-US">&bull; Be a fan of action games. Having played many different types of games is a plus<br />
</span><span lang="EN-US">&bull; Know how to setup and problem-solve hardware and office software on PC clients running Windows Vista Ultimate<br />
</span><span lang="EN-US">&bull; Understanding how networks work. LAN, WLAN, Internet, firewalls, servers, TCP/IP, DHCP and DNS<br />
</span><span lang="EN-US">&bull; Must know how to find, install and troubleshoot drivers on Windows Vista<br />
</span><span lang="EN-US">&bull; Service minded and customer focused<br />
</span><span lang="EN-US">&bull; Previous knowledge of Microsoft Windows Server and Debian Linux is a plus<br />
</span><span lang="EN-US"><br />
If you are interested in the position, send a cover letter and CV via our web form or e-mail.</span></p></span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="column_nav">
        <span class="column_nav_cat">Contact</span>
        <p>
          Please send your application through the online form below, or by regular mail to
          our physical adress. If you prefer to send your application by email click
          <a href="&#109;&#97;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;&#58;&#105;&#116;&#113;&#97;&#64;&#103;&#114;&#105;&#110;&#46;&#115;&#101;">here</a>.</p>
